title: Rat Scratch Fever [2011 - USA] science fiction horror

Rat Scratch Fever (2011 - USA)

Horror / Science Fiction
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1311083/


Michael W. Schwibs Productions

Bare Bones International Film Festival - WON - Best Visual Effects

Made on a budget of cheeseburgers and good intentions Jeff Leroy's schlock masterpiece Rat Scratch Fever is one the greatest feats of cinematic ingenuity thus far this century. A veteran in the world of low-budget horror and softcore skin flicks, director Leroy throws everything in his resourceful arsenal (and garage) at the screen for this staggering, entertaining tale of astronauts that bring back humungoid mutant rats to a City of Los Angeles just waiting to be demolished by their feverish claws. The result is a mash-up of alien invasion, animal disaster and mega-action that boggles the mind, hammers the senses and fulfills all expectations.
